{"type": "article", "id": 4658, "title": "Stellio 攀岩保护绳固定器", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-24T07:32:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233439giJRfB3Qds16couF.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tStellio 攀岩保护绳固定器是来自印度普纳的设计师 Anupreeta Agate 的作品。她从壁虎的特性与外形中得到了灵感，设计了这款抽象派壁虎造型的攀岩利器，选用 Geckotape 与 Geckskin 的合成材料，内含强力吸盘。攀岩时，你只需将这款固定器往岩石表面一拍一压，就能牢牢吸附在岩石上，待需要继续向前挪动位置时，你用力一拽，Stellio 就会离开岩石，再固定在合适的位置即可，方便又省力。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233436KtTOwNxPzYaFnvi9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.775\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233437ocn2UqTlEgzrj4ey.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.490625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233437ULYeAR0yBVEihWMb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.91875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233437VZluSwMQxs9Cay3Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5984375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233438GLYlEiHzDdMXu14S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6796875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}